"The next big thing":	"下一个重大变革",
"#NextBig-Head-p01":	"游戏开发中的",
"#NextBig-Head-p02":	"区块链技术革命",

"Raise funds and develop an “economic community”":	"众筹开发，打造玩家的经济社会",
"Bypass traditional funding models and raise funds to develop your game from hundreds or even thousands of individuals by offering them real value, for example rare in-game items.":	"绕过传统的筹资模型，通过向成千上百个玩家提供游戏内资产等拥有真实价值的物品，为游戏开发筹资。",
"Take advantage of all off-the-shelf developers’ tools offered by the Hoard platform.":	"运用Hoard平台提供的立即可用的开发商工具。",
"If HRD tokens are not sufficiently flexible for your desired business model, come up with your own innovative token designs. Tweak existing ownership models, offer token holders access to unique items and features, or even get them engaged in decisions regarding future development of your game.":	"如果HRD的代币对于你的理想而言尚显不足，你也可以自己设计代币，调整既有的所有权模型，向代币持有者提供独特的物品与内容，甚至让他们参与到决策中，共同制定游戏开发的未来。",
"The token distribution represents a new kind of incentivized community which you can activate and engage in all kinds of new ways.":	"代币的流通将带动起全新的游戏社区，开发商也能以各种新方式拉动社区，与其互动。",

