"Introduce new content to existing games to extend their economic viability.":	"给既有游戏注入新内容，扩展其收益性。",

"New forms of product design and accompanying marketing models":	"全新的产品设计形式将带来全新的营销方式",
"Enjoy network effects by launching multiple games and platforms with interdependent features and take advantage of synergies with other titles on the Hoard platform.":	"发挥互联效应，同时发行彼此互联的多款游戏，或与其他Hoard平台上的游戏联动。",
"Access Hoard’s platform-wide marketing and advertising tools, or come up with your own methods, backed right into your token design. Engage in supportive activities (e.g. web minigames) which enable gamers to acquire items, create charity campaigns (“mining gold for goods”), etc.":	"开发商可以使用Hoard平台的一系列营销与广告工具，或在代币设计中融入自己的商务理念，比如通过辅助性活动（如网络迷你游戏）让玩家获得物品，或提供优惠（比如挖金矿）等。",




