"Take extensive advantage of decentralized cryptocurrency exchange":	"充分发挥去中心化加密货币交易的各项优势",
"Birds’ eye view of your game’s item and money economy":	"对游戏物品与游戏内经济活动一目了然",
"Easy plugin integrations with Unity and Unreal Engine":	"与Unity、Unreal Engine的简易插件式整合",
"Include smart wallet and third-party integrations":	"支持智能钱包与第三方整合",
"Abstract the complexities of blockchain technology":	"对复杂的区块链技术进行抽象精简",
"Standalone SDK in multiple languages":	"支持多种语言的独立SDK",
"Secure payment gateways":	"安全的支付门户",
"Includes secure dashboards":	"支持安全面板",
"100% free and open source SDK":	"100%免费与开放源码的SDK",




