"We’ve implemented a non-fungible solution for Plasma MVP and are building an SDK that will make it easy for game developers to integrate blockchain technology into their games.":	"我们针对Plasma MVP提供了非同质的解决方案，并开发了方便开发商在游戏中引入区块链技术的SDK。",
